    <div class="subheader">Synopsis</div>
    
    
      <div class="description padded"><p>Police said there were three separate shootings in Canada's capital, prompting a lockdown at Parliament Hill on Oct. 22, 2014. Authorities confirmed shots had been fired inside Parliament, at the National War Memorial and near the Rideau Centre shopping mall. - <a href="http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/gunman-killed-in-ottawa-3-shootings-confirmed-1.2065443#ixzz3GtGIyOG9">CTV News</a></strong></p></div>
    
  

  

  
