ethods within a given society. History of political thought can be traced back to early antiquity, with seminal works such as Plato's <i>Republic<\/i>, Aristotle's <i>Politics<\/i> and the works of Confucius.<\/p>","image_height":788,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T00:39:46.820818"}]},{"push_content":"Speaking at Cpl. Nathan Cirillo's funeral service, Canadian Prime Minister Stephen Harper says, 'Our hearts are broken' - @BBCBreaking","shortened_url":"http:\/\/bit.ly\/1zERPgN","id":458632,"type":"text","author":{"username":"tricia.mcdermott","id":23,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/user\/23\/","email":"Tricia.McDermott@nbcuni.com","last_name":"McDermott","first_name":"Tricia","is_staff":true,"full_name":"Tricia McDermott"},"permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/10\/28\/speaking-at-cpl-nathan-cirillos-funeral-service","media":null,"url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BBCBreaking\/status\/527136224348483584","content":"Speaking at Cpl. Nathan Cirillo's funeral service, Canadian Prime Minister Stephen Harper says, 'Our hearts are broken' - @BBCBreaking","date_ap":"Oct 28, 2014, 04:37 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/458632\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/10\/28\/speaking-at-cpl-nathan-cirillos-funeral-service","pushed":true,"data_type":null,"submitter":"editor","tweet":{"content":"\"Our hearts are broken,\" Canada PM says at funeral of #OttawaShooting victim Cpl Nathan Cirillo http:\/\/t.co\/Zoqv8C8Ym3","url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BBCBreaking\/status\/527136224348483584","id":258002,"user_id":"5402612","screen_name":"BBCBreaking","resource_uri":"","name":"BBC Breaking News","location":"London, UK","avatar":"http:\/\/pbs.twimg.com\/profile_images\/460740982498013184\/wIPwMwru_normal.png","tweet_id":"527136224348483584","date":"2014-10-28T16:34:04"},"data":null,"short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/i\/B5TS","slug":"speaking-at-cpl-nathan-cirillos-funeral-service","updated_date":"2014-10-28T16:37:35.182646","note":n