and co-workers, he had previously expressed support for jihadists and others in the Middle East resisting the West's intervention, but was not known to the police to be a terrorism risk. In his mother's opinion, the attack was the \"last desperate act\" of someone with a mental disorder who felt trapped.<\/p>\n<p>Classified by the RCMP as a \"terrorist attack\", it was the most serious security breach at Parliament Hill since the 1966 parliament bombing. It took place two days after a man used his car to run over two Canadian soldiers in Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, killing one. The two incidents, which attracted international attention, raised concerns about the effectiveness of police actions to prevent terrorist attacks, the prevention of radicalization and the security measures in-place at federal and provincial legislatures. The Canadian government had already prepared a bill to expand the powers and courtroom anonymity and surveillance powers of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service (CSIS), Canada's spy agency, which was due to be introduced the day of the shootings, and was postponed by the event. The government plans to introduce new anti-terrorism measures. Security at Parliament Hill is to be stepped up.<\/p>","image_height":2544,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2014-10-28T16:37:32.533526"},{"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=43347","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=43347","id":43347,"created_on":"2013-08-27T17:48:48.047468","recent_count":1,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/f\/f7\/ObituariesontheWall.jpg","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/obituaries\/","daily_count":1,"trend_rank_last":0,"muted_by_default":false,"woeid":null,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/43347\/","local_url":"\/topic\/obituaries\/","placetype":"","links":"","kind":"vertical","name":"obituaries","category":"Topic","short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/t\/LRJ","wikipedia_url":"http:\/\/en.