h civil procedure.<\/p>","image_height":900,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T01:14:53.150744"},{"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=2","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=2","id":2,"created_on":"2012-10-23T22:09:19","recent_count":4,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/6\/6a\/Inglehart_Values_Map.svg","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/politics\/","daily_count":58,"trend_rank_last":2,"muted_by_default":false,"woeid":null,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/2\/","local_url":"\/topic\/politics\/","placetype":"","links":"","kind":"vertical","name":"politics","category":"Topic","short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/t\/C","wikipedia_url":"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politics","twitter_username":"breakingpol","slug":"politics","facebookchat":"","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politics\">Wikipedia<\/a>","latitude":null,"active":true,"item_count":52674,"image_width":802,"trend_rank_current":2,"longitude":null,"livevideo":"","description":"<p><b>Politics<\/b> (from Greek:  <i>politikos<\/i>, meaning \"of, for, or relating to citizens\") is the practice and theory of influencing other people on a global, civic or individual level. More narrowly, it refers to achieving and exercising positions of governance  organized control over a human community, particularly a state. Furthermore, politics is the study or practice of the distribution of power and resources within a given community (a hierarchically organized population) as well as the interrelationship(s) between communities. A variety of methods are employed in politics, which include promoting one's own political views among people, negotiation with other political subjects, making laws, and exercising force, including warfare against adversaries. Politics is exercised on a wide range of social levels, from clans and tribes of traditional societies, through modern local governments, companies and institutions up to sovereign states, to the international level.<\/p>\n<p>A political system is a framework which defines acceptable political methods within a given society. History of political thought can be traced back to early antiquity, with seminal works such as Plato's <i>Republic<\/i>, Aristotle's <i>Politics<\/i> and the works of Confucius.<\/p>","image_height":788,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T00:39:46.820818"}]},{"push_content":"State Department: Secretary John Kerry traveling to Ottawa tomorrow for bilateral meetings, to convey condolences following last week's attacks in Canada - @marieharf","shortened_url":"http:\/\/bit.ly\/1wvEYch","id":458159,"type":"text","author":{"username":"stephanie.clary","id":8,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/user\/8\/","email":"stephanie.clary@breakingnews.com","last_name":"Clary","first_name":"Stephanie","is_staff":true,"full_name":"Stephanie Clary"},"permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/10\/27\/state-department-secretary-john-kerry-traveling-t","media":null,"url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/marieharf\/status\/526791178696806400","content":"State Department: Secretary John Kerry traveling to Ottawa tomorrow for bilateral meetings, to convey condolences following last week's attacks in Canada - @marieharf","date_ap":"Oct 27, 2014, 05:47 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/458159\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/10\/27\/state-department-secretary-john-kerry-traveling-t","pushed":true,"data_type":null,"submitter":"editor","tweet":{"content":"TRAVEL UPDATE: @JohnKerry travelling to Ottawa tomorrow for bilateral mtgs &amp; to convey condolences following last weeks attacks in Canada","url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/marieharf\/status\/526791178696806400","id":257655,"user_id":"161427200","screen_name":"marieharf","resource_uri":"","name":"Marie Harf","location":"Washington, DC","avatar":"http:\/\/pbs.twimg.com\/profile_images\/378800000856203067\/ae3fc77396607f34a6fcd0ae870c38bb_norm