ain exceptions (strict liability).<\/p>\r\n<p>While every crime violates the law, not every violation of the law counts as a crime. Breaches of private law (torts and breaches of contract) are not automatically punished by the state, but can be enforced through civil procedure.<\/p>","image_height":900,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T01:14:53.150744"},{"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=2","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=2","id":2,"created_on":"2012-10-23T22:09:19","recent_count":4,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/6\/6a\/Inglehart_Values_Map.svg","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/politics\/","daily_count":58,"trend_rank_last":2,"muted_by_default":false,"woeid":null,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/2\/","local_url":"\/topic\/politics\/","placetype":"","links":"","kind":"vertical","name":"politics","category":"Topic","short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/t\/C","wikipedia_url":"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politics","twitter_username":"breakingpol","slug":"politics","facebookchat":"","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politics\">Wikipedia<\/a>","latitude":null,"active":true,"item_count":52674,"image_width":802,"trend_rank_current":2,"longitude":null,"livevideo":"","description":"<p><b>Politics<\/b> (from Greek:  <i>politikos<\/i>, meaning \"of, for, or relating to citizens\") is the practice and theory of influencing other people on a global, civic or individual level. More narrowly, it refers to achieving and exercising positions of governance  organized control over a human community, particularly a state. Furthermore, politics is the study or practice of the distribution of power and resources within a given community (a hierarchically organized population) as well as the interrelationship(s) between communities. A variety of methods are employed in politics, which include promoting one's own political views among people, negotiation with other political subjects, making laws, and exercising force, including warfare against adversaries. Politics is exercised on a wide range of social levels, from clans and tribes of traditional societies, through modern local governments, companies and institutions up to sovereign states, to the international level.<\/p>\n<p>A political system is a framework which defines acceptable political methods within a given society. History of political thought can be traced back to early antiquity, with seminal works such as Plato's <i>Republic<\/i>, Aristotle's <i>Politics<\/i> and the works of Confucius.<\/p>","image_height":788,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T00:39:46.820818"}]},{"push_content":"More: Police investigating Ottawa shooter's interactions with individuals before attack; focus on whether interactions facilitated 'terrorist attack' - @rcmpgrcpolice","shortened_url":"http:\/\/bit.ly\/1yDreN0","id":457843,"type":"text","author":{"username":"jillian.stamper","id":14,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/user\/14\/","email":"Jillian.Stampher@nbcuni.com","last_name":"Stampher","first_name":"Jillian","is_staff":true,"full_name":"Jillian Stampher"},"permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/10\/26\/more-police-investigating-ottawa-shooters-intera","media":null,"url":"http:\/\/www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca\/news-nouvelles\/speeches-stat-discours-decl\/2014\/20141026-eng.htm?tw","content":"More: Police investigating Ottawa shooter's interactions with individuals before attack; focus on whether interactions facilitated 'terrorist attack' - @rcmpgrcpolice","date_ap":"Oct 26, 2014, 11:01 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/457843\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/10\/26\/more-police-investigating-ottawa-shooters-intera","pushed":true,"data_type":null,"submitter":"editor","tweet":null,"data":null,"short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/i\/B5Gj","slug":"more-police-investigating-ottawa-shooters-intera","updated_date":"2014-10-26T