ch as scoring goals or crossing a line first, or by the determination of judges who are scoring elements of the sporting performance, including objective or subjective measures such as technical performance or artistic impression.<\/p>\n<p>In organised sport, records of performance are often kept, and for popular sports, this information may be widely announced or reported in sport news. In addition, sport is a major source of entertainment for non-participants, with spectator sport drawing large crowds to venues, and reaching wider audiences through broadcasting.<\/p>\n<p>According to A.T. Kearney, a consultancy, the global sporting industry is worth up to $620 billion as of 2013.<\/p>","image_height":1419,"geohash":"","latest_item_date":"2015-03-24T00:02:07.921868"}]},{"push_content":"Photo: 2 Ottawa police with automatic weapons stand guard at the National War Memorial surrounded by flowers placed in honor of fallen soldier - @HannahThibedeau","shortened_url":"http:\/\/bit.ly\/1pLH2rv","id":457561,"type":"text","author":{"username":"aaron.edwards","id":17,"resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/user\/17\/","email":"aaron.edwards@nbcuni.com","last_name":"Edwards","first_name":"Aaron","is_staff":false,"full_name":"Aaron Edwards"},"permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/10\/25\/photo-2-ottawa-police-with-automatic-weapons-stan","media":{"width":900,"height":1199,"author_name":"HannahThibedeau","url":"https:\/\/pbs.twimg.com\/media\/B00VFmgIEAAOLei.jpg:large","title":"Hannah Thibedeau on Twitter: \"2 Ottawa police w automatic weapons on either side of guard at the National War Memorial #ottawashooting #cdnpoli #hw http:\/\/t.co\/EncwIn99Vn\"","id":52689,"thumbnail_url":"https:\/\/pbs.twimg.com\/media\/B00VFmgIEAAOLei.jpg:thumb","thumbnail_width":150,"type":"photo","resource_uri":"","author_url":"http:\/\/twitter.com\/HannahThibedeau","provider_url":"http:\/\/twitter.com","provider_name":"Twitter","original_url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/HannahThibedeau\/status\/5260